{"tid":1876881,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方查星火同盟洗黑錢案再拘捕四人涉販毒","createTime":"2020-02-12T16:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T18:18:58.000Z","uid":67089,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1a70b13afeb3d4a2f47c68742725f287992cadb2","tid":1876881,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"警方因應去年12月網上眾籌平台星火同盟涉及的洗黑錢案, 對涉案空殼公司的可疑財務活動進行調查, 再拘捕四人.<br />\n        警方調查發現, 一個與有關空殼公司有銀行轉帳交易的戶口持有人, 涉及販毒活動. 而這個銀行戶口亦有其他不尋常的可疑交易紀錄. 經進一步調查, 警方昨晚在石硤尾南山邨, 以販毒及洗黑錢罪名, 拘捕這名戶口持有人, 被捕男子18歲, 報稱無業.<br />\n        另外, 警方在行動中, 也以藏毒罪名拘捕一男兩女毒品買家, 他們年齡介乎26至35歲, 分別報稱是貨車司機, 公關和無業, 並檢獲少量毒品包括氯胺酮, 可卡因及大麻, 市值約8千元.<br />\n        警方說, 會循多方面繼續調查, 特別會針對有關戶口用途和資金流向, 也會追查背後是否有人操控, 以及有關毒品來源, 不排除有更多人被捕.<br />\n       <a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20200212194043&amp;page=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FSearchText%3D%26NewsId%3D20200212194043%26page%3D0&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=746d230c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20200212194043&amp;page=0</a><br />\n<br />\n班曱甴柒完一單又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150de7b10b627e117f1a48cff2529b2f9ff4fd0d","tid":1876881,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070743&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=498d8285\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070743&h=142310b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070743</a>"},{"pid":"239697f990984431cacc